<bibRefCitation id="29DCC5E68DF0E823EBA4575D1B5796F1" author="Alex, JF" pageId="106" pageNumber="107" refId="B4" refString="Alex, JF, Cayoutte, R, Mulligan, GA, 1980. Common and botanical names of weeds in Canada/Noms populaire et scientifiques des plantes nuisables du Canada. Ontario Publication 1397. Canadian Department of Agriculture, Ottawa." title="Common and botanical names of weeds in Canada / Noms populaire et scientifiques des plantes nuisables du Canada. Ontario Publication 1397. Canadian Department of Agriculture, Ottawa." year="1980">Alex et al. 1980</bibRefCitation>
